                  </hi>. (<hi rend="italic">Policeman, K</hi> 381). I produce a certificate—(<hi rend="italic">Read</hi>: "<hi rend="italic">Central Criminal Court; John Jones, Convicted, Aug.</hi>, 1852, <hi rend="italic">of stealing a handkerchief from the person; 
Confined one year</hi>")—I was present at the trial; M'Quade is the person.</p>
